
Project headers are grouped by responsibility:

```text
app/        application orchestration
config/     pins, defaults, limits
domain/     settings and testable control logic
hardware/   ESP32 hardware adapters
storage/    persistence adapters
ui/         OLED view
web/        dashboard server and generated pages
```

Prefer includes that show the layer explicitly, for example:

```cpp
#include "domain/TemperatureLogic.h"
#include "hardware/RelayModule.h"
```
